              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Absolute neutron flux was determined by a small",
                "  parallel plate 238U fission chamber.",
                " The abundance of the 238U sample was better than",
                "  99.997%.",
                " The mass of the 238U sample was 547.2 +/- 7.1 ug,",
                "  the diameter was 2.0 cm.",
                " The working gas fission chamber is flowing Ar+2.85%",
                "  CO2 gas at a pressure slightly higher than 1.0 atm."
              ]
            }
